---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 355
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Act and Essence
By: Tauler
---
Children, could we but truly stand in this holy of holies for an hour
or a moment, it were a thousand times better and more profitable for
us, and more pleasing and praiseworthy in the sight of the Eternal
God, than forty years spent in your own self-imposed tasks.
